<p sourcefile="en/running-your-store/vendor-management.md" sourcestartlinenumber="67"><img src="_static/vendor-management/vendor4.png" sourcefile="en/running-your-store/vendor-management.md" sourcestartlinenumber="67" alt="Display"></p>
