<h3 id="catalog" sourcefile="en/running-your-store/vendor-management.md" sourcestartlinenumber="137">Catalog</h3>
<p sourcefile="en/running-your-store/vendor-management.md" sourcestartlinenumber="139">In the <em sourcefile="en/running-your-store/vendor-management.md" sourcestartlinenumber="139">Catalog</em> panel, define the following vendor settings:
<img src="_static/vendor-management/vendorsettings2.png" sourcefile="en/running-your-store/vendor-management.md" sourcestartlinenumber="140" alt="Catalog"></p>
<ul sourcefile="en/running-your-store/vendor-management.md" sourcestartlinenumber="142">
